          "audioFile": "orion_match_start_doorman_orion_convo02_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/orion_match_start_doorman_orion_convo02_01.mp3",
          "text": "How are things at The Baroness?",
          "duration": 1.848
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_doorman_orion_convo02_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_doorman_orion_convo02_02.mp3",
          "text": "They've been running smoothly since The Baxter Society's intervention.",
          "duration": 3.712
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Grey talon",
          "audioFile": "orion_match_start_doorman_orion_convo02_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/orion_match_start_doorman_orion_convo02_03.mp3",
          "text": "That's good to hear.",
          "duration": 1.076
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_doorman_orion_convo02_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_doorman_orion_convo02_04.mp3",
          "text": "It is.  There are some sins that not even bottomless mimosas can make up for.",
          "duration": 5.267
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "doorman_grey talon_convo03",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Grey talon",
          "audioFile": "orion_match_start_doorman_orion_convo03_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/orion_match_start_doorman_orion_convo03_01.mp3",
          "text": "The Baroness still the most haunted hotel in America?",
          "duration": 2.833
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_doorman_orion_convo03_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_doorman_orion_convo03_02.mp3",
          "text": "Just the tri-state area I'm afraid, that ghastly business in Macomb pulled a lot of midwest specters.",
          "duration": 7.741
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Grey talon",
          "audioFile": "orion_match_start_doorman_orion_convo03_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/orion_match_start_doorman_orion_convo03_03.mp3",
          "text": "Sorry.",
          "duration": 0.647
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_doorman_orion_convo03_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_doorman_orion_convo03_04.mp3",
          "text": "It's fine.  I imagine today will put things back on track.",
          "duration": 3.76
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "doorman_victor_convo01",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_frank_doorman_convo01_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_frank_doorman_convo01_01.mp3",
          "text": "After the ritual you should stop by The Baroness - our house tailor is top notch should any part of you\u2026 pop loose.",
          "duration": 8.648
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Victor",
          "audioFile": "frank_match_start_frank_doorman_convo01_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/frank_match_start_frank_doorman_convo01_02.mp3",
          "text": "That place might be a little fancy for someone like me",
          "duration": 3.121
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_frank_doorman_convo01_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_frank_doorman_convo01_03.mp3",
          "text": "Oh The Baroness does not discriminate my friend.  I assure you that you will be well taken care of.",
          "duration": 6.232
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
